               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17530111-32-off161-c321" targOrder="Y" targets="t17530111-32-defend383 t17530111-32-off161 t17530111-32-verdict164"></join>
         
               <p>92. (L.) 
               <persName id="t17530111-32-defend383" type="defendantName">
                  Edward 
                  Wilson 
               <interp inst="t17530111-32-defend383" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-defend383" type="given" value="Edward"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-defend383" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , was indicted for <rs id="t17530111-32-off161" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-off161" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-off161" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing one silk handkerchief value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17530111-32-victim385" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Piggot 
                        <interp inst="t17530111-32-victim385" type="surname" value="Piggot"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17530111-32-victim385" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17530111-32-victim385" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17530111-32-off161 t17530111-32-victim385"></join>
                     </persName>
                      
                  , from his person
            </rs>, <rs id="t17530111-32-cd162" type="crimeDate">December 16</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17530111-32-off161 t17530111-32-cd162"></join> ++</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17530111-32-person386">
                  John 
                  Piggot 
               <interp inst="t17530111-32-person386" type="surname" value="Piggot"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-person386" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-person386" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming along Snow-Hill on the 16th of December last about six in the evening, and at the end of a place called <placeName id="t17530111-32-crimeloc163">Ten Bells Court</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17530111-32-crimeloc163" type="placeName" value="Ten Bells Court"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17530111-32-crimeloc163" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17530111-32-off161 t17530111-32-crimeloc163"></join> there were the prisoner and two other men came near me, I felt something tug at my pocket, so I looked and saw the prisoner's hand in it, he snatch'd my handkerchief out and gave it to the other two, and they both ran away. I secured the prisoner immediately and took him to the sign of the Swan and sent for a constable, who took him to the Compter, and from thence before my lord mayor, who committed him to Newgate.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="175301110033"></xptr>Prisoner's Defence</p>
               <p>I was on the other side of the way going down to Field lane, and the prosecutor called after me and said, kip, so I turned about and asked him what he wanted with me; he said I had picked his pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17530111-32-verdict164" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-verdict164" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-verdict164" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17530111-32-punish165" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17530111-32-punish165" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17530111-32-defend383 t17530111-32-punish165"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
